<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>', 'Construction of Thirty Meter Telescope put on hold AGAIN', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-03 09:05:08', '2015-12-03 09:05:08', '', '44', 'http://test-tasks.local/primary/?p=52', '0', 'revision', '', '0' );
