<p style="text-align: justify;">Last posts in Stories category [category slug="english"]</p>', 'Construction of Thirty Meter Telescope put on hold AGAIN', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-04 00:45:26', '2015-12-04 00:45:26', '', '44', 'http://test-tasks.local/primary/?p=77', '0', 'revision', '', '0' );
